<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>SILENT NIGHT</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Zan thieng thip laitak in,
 Vakna a hungtung tai;
 Vawnsen a chawi chun nunnem in,
 Nau thiengtho ngilnei leh zainem,
 Chamna Lal Cha chu,
 Chamna Lal Cha chu.

[V2]
 2. Zan thiengthip laitak in,
 Puipa Si-al vak hawih;
 Michingte chun hun zuizel in,
 Thilpiek thiengtho chu a pieu hi,
 Lalpa Krista chu,
 Lalpa Krista chu.

[V3]
 3. Zie zan thip laitak chun,
 Si-al minthang vakin;
 Van Angelte zaila hawih chun,
 Halleluijah, I Lalpen uh,
 Lalpa Krista chu,
 Lalpa Krista chu.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>61</hymn_number>
</song>